imdb.plot outline: Biz 1 on 1 with Randy Lennon is a one on one interview show that tells the compelling stories of the most interesting executives and companies in North America. Each week, host Randy Lennon sits down with the CEO/Founder of three diverse businesses and interviews them about their vision, passion, and experiences building and running their company. From startups to third generation family enterprises, the show covers a wide array of stories from coast to coast.
